#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>&kmail; Welcome Screen</para>"
msgstr "<para>&kmail; Pozdravni zaslon</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kmail; Team welcomes you to &kmail;, a user-friendly email client by "
"&kde;. Our goal is to make &kmail; a program that is both beautiful and "
"intuitive without sacrificing power."
msgstr ""
"Ekipa &kmail;-a vas pozdravlja v &kmail;, uporabniku prijaznem odjemalcu e-"
"pošte podjetja &kde;. Naš cilj je ustvariti &kmail; program, ki je lep in "
"intuitiven, ne da bi pri tem žrtvovali njegovo moč."

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have never set up an email client on a &UNIX; system before, we "
"suggest that you read through the <link linkend=\"getting-started\">Getting "
"Started</link> section first."
msgstr ""
"Če pred tem še nikoli niste nastavlja e-poštnega odjemalca na sistemu "
"&UNIX;, priporočamo branje poglavja<link linkend=\"getting-started\">Kako "
"začeti</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: intro.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Some &kmail; Features"
msgstr "Nekatere lastnosti &kmail;-a"

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here is a brief guide to some of the great features available in &kmail;"
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je kratek vodnik po nekaterih od množice dobrih lastnosti, ki so na "
"voljo za &kmail;"

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You do not have to use your mouse when working with &kmail;. Everything can "
"be done with <link linkend=\"keyboard-shortcuts\">Keyboard Shortcuts</link>."
msgstr ""
"Pri delu s programom &kmail; vam ni treba uporabljati miške. Vse lahko "
"naredite z <link linkend=\"keyboard-shortcuts\">Tipkovnimi bližjicami</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Although &kmail; is very reliable, you should keep backups of your messages, "
"&ie;, use one of the export/archive options listed in <link linkend=\"backups"
"\">Backup Options</link> to back up your settings and email regularly."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav je &kmail; zelo zanesljiv, morate hraniti varnostne kopije svojih "
"sporočil, &ie;, uporabite eno od možnosti izvoza/arhiviranja, navedenih v "
"<link linkend=\"backups\">Možnosti varnostnega kopiranja</link> za redno "
"varnostno kopiranje nastavitev in e-pošte."

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; makes it easy to import email from many different email "
"applications. The options are described in <link linkend=\"import-restore"
"\">Restore and Import in &kmail;</link>."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; omogoča enostaven uvoz e-pošte iz različnih e-poštnih aplikacij. "
"Možnosti so opisane v <link linkend=\"import-restore\">Obnovitev in uvoz v "
"&kmail;</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can separate your messages into different categories by using &kmail;'s "
"extensive <link linkend=\"folders\">Folders</link> options. Features include "
"special handling for specified folders: mailing lists, acl (&IMAP; only), "
"and archiving."
msgstr ""
"Sporočila lahko razdelite v različne kategorije z uporabo obsežnih možnosti "
"<link linkend=\"folders\">Mape</link> v storitvi &kmail;. Funkcije "
"vključujejo posebno obravnavo določenih map: poštni seznami, acl (samo "
"&IMAP;) in arhiviranje."

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can complement your folder setup with highly configurable <link linkend="
"\"filters\">filters</link>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitev mape lahko dopolnite z visoko nastavljivimi <link linkend="
"\"filters\">filtri</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default &kmail; will detect common email <link linkend=\"configure-"
"security-email-scams\">scams</link>. You can also fight SPAM and viruses by "
"creating filters that work with external programs to scan email as it comes "
"in. See <link linkend=\"the-anti-spam-wizard\">Anti Spam</link> and <link "
"linkend=\"the-anti-virus-wizard\">Anti Virus</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto bo &kmail; zaznal običajne e-poštne <link linkend=\"configure-"
"security-email-scams\">prevare</link>. Proti nezaželeni pošti in virusom se "
"lahko borite tudi tako, da ustvarite filtre, ki v sodelovanju z zunanjimi "
"programi pregledujejo prejeto e-pošto. Za podrobnosti glejte <link linkend="
"\"the-anti-spam-wizard\">Proti neželeni pošti</link> in <link linkend=\"the-"
"anti-virus-wizard\">Proti virusom</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It's easy to manage several email accounts by using different <link linkend="
"\"configure-identity\">identities</link>."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo različnih <link linkend=\"configure-identity\">identitet</link> "
"lahko preprosto upravljate več e-poštnih računov."

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "We hope you will enjoy &kmail;!"
msgstr "Upamo, da boste s &kmail;om zadovoljni!"

#. Tag: title
#: intro.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Getting Help"
msgstr "Pridobivanje pomoči"

#. Tag: para
#: intro.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail;'s homepage can be found at <ulink url=\"https://apps.kde.org/kmail2/"
"\">https://apps.kde.org/kmail2/</ulink>. There you will find useful links "
"(&eg;, to the user and developer mailing lists, and to the community wiki "
"pages.) Please report any bugs in &kmail; using <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Report Bug...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Domačo stran &kmail; najdete na <ulink url=\"https://apps.kde.org/kmail2/"
"\">https://apps.kde.org/kmail2/</ulink>. Tam boste našli koristne povezave "
"(&eg; do poštnih seznamov uporabnikov in razvijalcev ter do strani skupnosti "
"wiki). Prosimo, prijavite morebitne napake v &kmail; z uporabo "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prijavi napako...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

